commit.message:
Method.java (hashCode): Use getName().

	* java/lang/reflect/Method.java (hashCode): Use getName().
	(toString): Likewise.
	* java/lang/reflect/natMethod.cc (getType): Initialize
	exception_types.

From-SVN: r35561
